# Upload File Version

# Description

Uploads a version of a file.

# Untitled Section

# Configuration

* 
* File - The file to get info for. Use the Folder icon to browse your Box folders and select a file.
* File - The content of the file to upload to Box. This field accepts IResource type input.









* Version ID - The ID of the file version that was uploaded. Automatically generated output variable.
* Upload file version - Automatically generated output variable.
